{"tid":2331682,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"咁多行業中，Design都算係性格比最撚差既一行","createTime":"2020-12-19T03:57:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T12:24:17.000Z","uid":119385,"like":103,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"2e6d1e23b866db4a4fe9803691f09ada9e5e8325","tid":2331682,"uid":119385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T03:57:21.000Z","msg":"要求高(Design真係好撚講天份，唔係人人做到)，唔通搵條廢毒撚都做到咩<br />\n而且靚仔靚女又多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係香港做呢行既待遇真係好撚差<br />\n萬頭人工(仲低過文員仔/掃街)，晚晚做到零晨兩三點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無OT錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地BIG4 OT都叫做為將來五六萬人工，<br />\n但呢行工時同BIG4一樣(甚至比BIG4更長，會計都有旺淡季，Design無，全年都咁peak)<br />\n人工上到二萬已經可以還神(其實而家好多無技能文員仔都20k)<br />\n<br />\n講真呢行既專業程度好媲比工程會計等行業，但點解香港會咁不受重視?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f40bb90e735e8b3edace360eaaaac1b4bb21852","tid":2331682,"uid":119385,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T03:57:40.000Z","msg":"自膠，性<strong>價</strong>比"},{"pid":"09d05a0e59db63a59aca834d960943f09f53c95c","tid":2331682,"uid":27210,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T03:58:40.000Z","msg":"點睇郭爾君"},{"pid":"50f383e9bdb01a0a2911503a7d90294aa86e855f","tid":2331682,"uid":85774,"like":8,"dislike":29,"score":-21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:01:32.000Z","msg":"Design ? 禁個制就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d30593b3e1b112108bc5017d21908b073a15e38","tid":2331682,"uid":73492,"like":40,"dislike":6,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:01:47.000Z","msg":"覺得設計有工程會計既專業<br />\n你係太高估設計定太唔清楚工程會計行業發展？"},{"pid":"90f1223e02718e27a9b6f7e5cf81c3e2758d1a75","tid":2331682,"uid":245813,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:02:41.000Z","msg":"多靚仔靚女做<br />